main event: Two objects were observed in the sky for 1 second, described as white with a greenish tinge moving rapidly.
interesting points: The objects were seen in a ground-visual observation,The undersides of the objects were lighter and flatter with marks similar to two half-moons,The observation likely pertained to a bolide that had already exploded,The sighting occurred on the night of April 30, 1957, at a residence in Seattle, The report was part of Project Blue Book, a U.S. Air Force program for investigating UFO sightings.
